{
  "stem": "23131.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When they'll come even the war's ending, where will they go?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who will they find?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Who will they see?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Where is their homes?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Where's their children?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Where's their wives?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- and the Germans were like-- some of them are like flies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they caught them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They killed them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They cut pieces from them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were screaming, for my children, for my brother, for my mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, it was terrible days before the liberation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They used to bring them on the base and make [INAUDIBLE] for them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- with all my pain, and with all my-- [SIGHS] with all my-- what I went, really, through, I just couldn't see the scene.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I couldn't be at the scene.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They used to cut their fingers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was an old man, Pupko.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He lived through the whole war with the whole family from Lida.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He took a piece of wood from the tree, and he was knocking the German, screaming, for my mother, for my father, for my children.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he wasn't the only one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was plenty others.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] We organized.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got a order from-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from the headquarters that we can leave the woods.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We organized.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We tried to pack up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Our suitcases weren't-- were not waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whatever who wants it to take, he took.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they lined them up, and in order, we went to Navaradok, because that was the closest from us, where it was giving to everyone a-- there was-- they made a big table there, that was already, more or less, a more-- more normal life than we had in the woods.",
      "word_count": 51
    }
  ],
